caption.title: Cellular functions and locations of differentially expressed proteins in GT1-7 cells after AAS exposure.
caption.p: (A) A total of 8 biological processes with their respective cellular locations (B) were categorized from 17 different proteins identified by mass spectrometry. Data were obtained from Uniprot database ( http://www.uniprot.org) and shown as percentages from the total number of proteins.
